Let's start at :55 and go for 15 minutes. If we start with short sprints, other people will be able to join in sooner.

Tagging ,@,darthchair,  and ,@,ShannonKJMurphy, 

It is TIME!  15 minutes!  WRITE!,pic.twitter.com/nicRl12UrS

FL:
I went back to Victoria’s side.  Her fingers no longer moved.  She’d closed her mouth, but she still looked as lifeless as the machinery behind her.
Thanks for the tag. My participation is TBD. I'll try to hop in when I can.
In a few hours, I'll probably start sprinting again when I've got laundry going. Maybe we can't all sprint together again then!
Oh, good. That might be better for me.
I might be able to do this.
I'll try to jump in on one lot two. I'm at work now, but I can sneak in 15 minutes here and there.
